description: As he suns himself out by the pool, Aspen notices new neighbor Dacotah Red spying on him from next door. Aspen is intrigued by Dacotah's curiosity and puts on a little show for him, which Dacotah definitely approves of, and once he's sure Dacotah's interested, Aspen calls him over. Dacotah makes his intentions apparent, and Aspen asks him if anyone saw him come over, because this is one neighborhood get together where the wives aren't invited.
title: Seeing Red
